caption.title: Percentage growth inhibition of tumor cell lines by propolis extracts obtained by conventional extraction (1) and ultrasound-assisted extraction (2): (A) HCT-116 (colon carcinoma), (B) HL-60 (leukemia), (C) PC3 (prostate carcinoma), and (D) SNB19 (glioblastoma).
caption.p: A1, B1, C1, D1, E1 and F1—Extracts obtained by conventional extraction; A2, B2, C2, D2, E2 and F2—Extracts obtained by ultrasound-assisted extraction. Statistical analysis: Values showing the same letter for the same analysis do not show significant differences (p>0.05) through the Tukey test at a 95% confidence level.
